    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus a toxic configuration of Chakra into your hand, which the touched creature's body reacts to as if it were poison. This technique delivers a contact poison with primary and secondary damage of 2d4 Constitution, and a save DC equal to this technique's.</p>\n\n\n\n",
